        "We're telling lies, and the one who tells the biggest lie will keep the cat.”\n\nThe old gentleman thought this was a good chance to teach the boys a useful lesson, so he said to them,“I've never told a lie in my life”.",
        "At once there was a great shout from all the boys, and they said,“You've won!",
